      "writtenOn": "2019-08-08T21:52:59Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "This function has no understanding of \u0027bytes\u0027, since it is not related to real proto messages at all really. It is just a formatter of starlark structs (not *Message) that makes them look like text-serialized proto. It is hosted in this file mostly by accident (to be accessible as \u0027proto.struct_to_textpb\u0027 from starlark) and I eagerly want to remove it.",
